      "raw_text": "Besides the gold saved from the\ntables car of high grade concen-\ntrates was recently shipped to the\nsmelter which Charles II. Wolf, Sec\nrotary Of tho company. estimates will\nnet practically $500. The smelter re-\nturns Of this shipment gave 500\nounces In sold and 1853 ounces in sill\nyer. Another car is now about ready\nfor shipment.\n\n\nThere has also been sacked 10 tons\nOF high grade concentrates that will\naverage $3.50 to the ton. A shipment\nVIII be made Just as soon as 70 tons\nare sacked. On the present basis Of\nreturns the mine will be producing\n$40. 900 per month."
